description.value:
A Trade agreement with the Alien Stryxis, giving +20 to all Interaction Tests to the bearer when dealing with Stryxis. The identity of the bearer is irrelevent, merely whomever presents it.

Requirements

A Rare Xeno Item, They are Good Craftsmanship by default, with no Poor or Common Craftsmanship versions. (if there are, they're probably fake)

Effect: Extremely Rare

Notes: -
